menu "imgui-sw configuration"

config IMGUISW_ENABLE_DIRTY_RECTS
    bool "Enable dirty-rects calculation (optimizes display updates)"
    default y
    help
        When enabled, the renderer tracks the union of clip rectangles per draw call
        and exposes them via callbacks to update only changed regions on the display.

config IMGUISW_AUTO_FLUSH
    bool "Automatically call flush callback after RenderDrawData()"
    default y
    help
        If a flush callback is set, call it automatically at the end of RenderDrawData().
        Disable to call ImGuiSW::Present() manually from your app.

endmenu
